---

<section class="flex min-h-[80vh] flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 text-center">
  <div data-animate class="animate-target space-y-6">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-text-primary to-text-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Raffaele Vasini
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary sm:text-xl">
      Full-Stack Developer · Backend &amp; Cloud
    </p>

    <p class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--width-prose)] text-base text-text-muted sm:text-lg">
      Trasformo requisiti di business in sistemi che funzionano — dal database alla pipeline.
    </p>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 pt-4">
      <a
        href="#projects"
        class="rounded-lg bg-accent px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-bg-primary transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover"
      >
        Vedi progetti
      </a>
      <a
        href="/docs"
        class="rounded-lg border border-border px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary transition-colors hover:border-border-hover hover:text-text-primary"
      >
        Documentazione
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
